social_posts.post_text: @driverinterviews  does awesome driver interviews at the track. Recently he did one on us. @littlelollie should have  just done the whole interview..She’s way easier to look at and joyful.—Link in my bio if you’d like to see my car and what we do #buckysltdracing

Legendary Vette guy Rod Saboury currently owns this Vette we painted 10-15 years ago. I forget exactly..it had been a Drag car since early 70s. Its great to see it at Timonium Md big show this weekend thanks for the great pics @dino_1sick_ford
Here’s some lettering from a while back for the guys at Kohrs Kustoms. A drag car they painted for the Biondo family. Sketch and go lettering is my fav style to do. #freehandlettering
Wonder if a kid got this for Christmas in 1940? #prewarschwinn#vintagechristmas
Have the Merriest Christmas #jesusisthereasonfortheseason

Got this Christmas helmet painted up for Jason lines son Jack..he will be piloting the @jesel_valvetrain truck at Bonneville this summer..used my signature @painthuffermetalflake square flake and kolor by @houseofkolor_  #buckysltdracing#competitionspecialist #teampainthuffer#houseofkolor

Thanks a lot to anyone who sent me something to paint at our shop or bought a sign this past year…means a lot to be trusted with someone’s pride and joy..hoping to keep making stuff pretty in 2023 #happynewyear
2023 I’m still a bicycle nerd..here’s one from 47 years ago. 76 Mongoose motomag as found #70sbmx#vintagebmx
@shakysullivan made this killer shirt for me when they were doing the Resto/build  on Bill Carter’s Tbird. Metal flake and all on the shirt. It lives in my lil shop/museum #shakydidit
Christmas commission Judy Lilly sign..always one of my favorite Greg of Akron paint jobs.it’s kinda genius

Another Christmas commissioned sign..these guys race killer Mopars. So I was definitely happy to make it for them #dragcarlettering

So after 3 seasons of racing with a stock white helmet. I started 2023 off jan1 painting my helmet.. my signature @painthuffermetalflake “Mineshaft” mix lights up in the sun #competionspecialist #mongoosebmx
Helmet action for fellow Line Performance team member in MN..thank you for your service. @painthuffermetalflake and custom @houseofkolor_ mixes #buckysltdracing #competitionspecialist
Here’s a Ram hood from a while back. @painthuffermetalflake and @houseofkolor_ products as always #buckysltd #custompaint
Thanks so much for this bicycle @mikebuff_ and @sebikes  I finally got to see the lettering i did for Buffs pro model in person..these ride amazing #sebikes#mikebuff
We’re finally on to the fun stuff for @line_5210 on her D stock Camaro #houseofkolor#buckysltd#stockeliminator

@shakysullivan made a neat post with @santinipaint talking about being inspired by other painters..it got me thinking about it again too..like we all “borrow” from other painters there was only one original custom painter..in a day of overused patterns and panels it’s clear people copy..with that said here’s some west coast style paint that I “stole” designs ect from Carter and many other drag boat painters..what makes a good custom painter tho is being inspired but being able to make it your own..Glen weisgerber told me one time “I wear Tom Kelly on my sleeve” I knew exactly what he meant
null
We’ve been at it on this D stock Camaro for @line_5210 here’s a few pics from first time in the sun #custompaint#buckysltd#competitionspecialist#teampainthuffer  @painthuffermetalflake

1976 Kenny Robert’s Grand national..this one is all my fav parts..1975 Redline fork..Redline first gen bars..second Gen redline gooseneck…early motomags. Probably top 3 rarest frames I have. I don’t even know why I have any but They sure are Tuff looking bikes #twowheeltuesday #70sbmx

I’ve been working on a Sox & Martin tribute car and it reminded me of this dart we got to help finish up for @exomodcarbon .. nothing gets me out of bed more than knowing a race car is in the shop..thanks for having me letter this factory light weight

Here it is..the East coast class you’ve been waiting on..my self and @fogiesspeedshop @montanezdesign are helping @painthuffermetalflake put on a 3 day workshop in Graham NC.price is $700 for the weekend DO NOT message me about paying ect. I have nothing in that. Message Brian @painthuffermetalflake please for info on paying and lodging.. in the classes I plan to help show how to do a clean layout efficiently and how to prep a job to last not just look good on Instagram.. we will touch on leaf application Pinstriping and I’ll show lettering basics to those that would like to give that a try ect..this will fun and laid back. No hero’s. Just come ready to learn and be inspired. We all are still learning. Me included. #painthufferclasses #teampainthuffer

I’m here on the east coast thinking how I wish I could have made the trip out to @dirtyfest ..Mayb next year. This one would been a fun one to ship out..this is Schwinn’s first attempt at a real bmx racing frame..1976 Competition full 4130 with hand brazed welds. 1 inch seat tube like a road bike..These were supposedly welded in the Paramount Road bike frame shop..these are pretty rare and this one has neat old custom paint #teamschwinn#70sbmx
Painted up this sk8deck from @skateboardconnection a few months ago.. @painthuffermetalflake as always

A few weeks ago @littlelollie and me took a long weekend to visit my friend @noble1tattooing at his @rightcoast_tattoo shop..started painting up his church pew..I did the windows like 4/5 years ago? I got a lil belly zap too from Todd. Always fun being there in his shop #handlettering #signpainting #tattoo
A few designs out now i lettered for @darkseas and @losermachine  Thanks always guys for having me be apart of the releases #handlettering
I spiffed up my 78 Mx250 and took it to a lil show today #vintagemx

Recently did the restoration paint and decals on my long time friends orig frame and fork..he recently got it back from his cousin who had it all these years. 1986 Dyno Compe  #80sfreetylebmx#saynotopowdercoat

@elbugsdidit and me are doing a custom lettering class with @painthuffermetalflake this will be focused on custom -freestyle lettering.if you’d like to learn how to sketch out lettering and make correct lettering styles here’s your chance. Dm @painthuffermetalflake to order your spot! #teampainthuffer

@elbugsdidit and me are doing a Kustom lettering class with @painthuffermetalflake this fall! Learn some freestyle lettering and basic sign layout..from beginner to experienced we are all still learning. DM @painthuffermetalflake to set up a spot
I’ve been cranking on my Dad @kingcuda new 4 speed car. If all goes well it should be pretty and fast @painthuffermetalflake @houseofkolor_
God Bless the USA #independenceday

Been non stop on Dads @kingcuda new Cuda. If all goes well it will be at Indy with him or Jason banging gears. Until then we have started a Facebook race team page “Hess hemi drag racing team”. If you’re on FB and interested lots of updates and buzz about the car on the group..Instagram is pretty much useless now in my opinion. So there will be many pics and videos on there in the future..as always thanks to Tom and Dave @houseofkolor_ and Brian @painthuffermetalflake for the support
Last clear is on..this week outlines then I hand it off to my Dad and crew ..thanks for the support @painthuffermetalflake @houseofkolor_ and @wbgoldleaf #hesshemidragracingteam

Spinning some gold on the Cuda the other week..I can’t do the constant drill running spin. I like to take my time and line up the spins and check them on real gold..many times I’ll go back over the spin to fix/brighten it  #wbgoldleaf

A few months ago we fixed up @line_5210 D stock Camaro after an unfortunate crash last year due to a suspension part breaking..this weekend first time back out she won Nhra best appearing at the Brainerd nationals..glad we got to help turn a tragic event into something pretty (scroll for Nhra video of the car) #buckysltd#competitionspecialist

@painthuffermetalflake East coast is in the books! What an amazing 3 days of class..I was blown away by the talent and how smoothly we got all the boards done..thanks a lot to @painthuffermetalflake for having me be apart of teaching the classes..Thanks to @houseofkolor_ and @reeddecorsey for the support. Great products produce great results. Until next time 🤙#teampainthuffer

The board I knocked out at the @painthuffermetalflake class this past weekend..we crushed it with every student getting their board done in 2 days..some students had never picked up a gun or brush before..that’s pretty amazing.
